{"tid":1477004,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日除左撳錢／集會之外，重有一樣好重要既事！！","createTime":"2019-08-16T03:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T09:53:19.000Z","uid":58883,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"42ade04d388115b7c266733d9f7f55c8b83facf1","tid":1477004,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:58:38.000Z","msg":"政府漠視民意，官黑勾結，利用警黑合作／白色恐怖等下流手段打擊市民言論自由。然而政府對市民傷亡不聞不問，只談經濟，由此可見，經濟係向政府施壓既其中一個有效手段。我地希望令政府唔好再用下流手段，正面回應民間五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n罷買可以好有效<br />\n如果香港有200萬人=2/7.5人口每星期少2日購物 = 2/7.5*2/7 = 少10%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，10%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。另外, 個人消費佔左香港GDP既68%, 如果少10%既消費就等於少左10%既GDP。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下一季度GPD再負增長,香港將進入Technical Recession。政府冇得唔理。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 (BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)<br />\n<br />\n罷買內容（好簡單）<br />\n1. 逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2. 逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n罷買運動正式開放宣誓承諾ＳＩＧＮ ＵＰ！已經快有10,000人簽左!!!!!!<br />\n我地需要每一個６１２出黎既２００萬人一齊幫手響應罷買行動。到時同政府講,我地有200萬人要攬炒!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">簽署ＬＩＮＫ 一定要簽</span></strong>!!<a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=9a412729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n#日五罷買 #罷買救港#Byebuyday<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日就係星期五,大家一定要提醒其他人減少消費!!突發緊急!!<br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=e05263a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\nIG PAGE <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=9840779f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\n罷買運動文字詳情 <a href=\"https://buyersstrike2019.wixsite.com/mysite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuyersstrike2019.wixsite.com%2Fmysite&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=f50283b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buyersstrike2019.wixsite.com/mysite</a><br />\n以前既ＰＯＳＴ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441419/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441419/page/1</a><br />\n金水ＦＢ ＰＯＳＴ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.233233693430128/2382386658514810/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fphotos%2Fa.233233693430128%2F2382386658514810%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=8bbd0a14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.233233693430128/2382386658514810/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"3bc3d27cfd4a25d12b7eee7a3187159fda86457a","tid":1477004,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"092e7675c8e5a8f6f8d1bad95f27782fcf4e6300","tid":1477004,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"PUSH ＃日五罷買"},{"pid":"adf5e728b065f7f93aa613acebaa21795026322d","tid":1477004,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fh