資產。<br />\n<br />\n對於一個連市民性命安危都無法保障的政府，我們不認為他們有能力捍衛龐大的聯繫匯率制度。<br />\n<br />\n故此，我們發起USD Challenge。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n「接受挑戰者，請到銀行或找換店換取至少1000蚊美元現鈔，拍照上傳至社交媒體，同時附上此段文字並標籤三名好友，向他們發起挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of Hongkongers embracing freedom and democracy.<br />\n<br />\nWe are currently oppressed by the China party state system. We don&rsquo;t want our deposits in bank becomes loans for Chinese enterprises. Such action is assisting tyrant to act brutally. Also, we don&rsquo;t believe that the communist regime in Hong Kong doesn&rsquo;t hold large portion of RMB assets through Exchange Funds. <br />\n<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t think that the Government is able to defend the huge Linked Exchange Rate System because the Government cannot even protect citizens&rsquo; lives.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, we launch USD Challenge.<br />\n<br />\nThe flow is as followed:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;To those who accept the challenge, please go to banks or exchange stores, get at least $1000 USD cash, take a photo and upload to any social media. At the same time, attach this paragraph, tag three friends and challenge them.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ba8efe7faac65bcbea81c1b7acc1b0ce02b81eeb","tid":1477004,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:13:29.000Z","msg":"不要說推 <br />\n試著說 <br />\n816㩒錢 816遮打 818見 ＃日五罷買<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=e05263a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a>"},{"pid":"26098fe528e2725a8b29ef4c0a26e1e6527f3b1c","tid":1477004,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:13:40.000Z","msg":"不要說推 <br />\n試著說 <br />\n816㩒錢 816遮打 818見 ＃日五罷買<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fby